\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The Southern Business School \'28Pty\'29 Ltd is registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training \'28DHET\'29 as a Private higher education institution and has programmes accredited by the Council on Higher Education \'28CHE\'29. \line \line The Institution is currently applying for the accreditation of a Diploma in Policing programme which will be offered in the distance mode of delivery from the Plot 10\'2FR28 Service Road\'2C Diswilmar\'2C Krugersdorp.\line \line The Institution has also applied for the accreditation of the following programmes which are still in process\'3A \line - Doctor of Policing H\'2FPR079\'2FE012CAN \'28Distance mode of delivery\'29\line - Bachelor of Laws H\'2FPR079\'2FE011CAN \'28Distance mode of delivery\'29\line \line During the HEQSF-alignment process\'2C the Institution submitted a Bachelor of Policing Practice \'28Contact\'2C Level 7\'2C minimum 394 Credits\'29 and Bachelor of Policing Practices \'28Honours\'29 \'28Contact\'2C Level 8\'2C minimum 120 Credits\'29 which were designated as Category C programmes. \line \line The Institution is registered to offer the following programmes\'3A\line - Bachelor of Policing Practice \line - Bachelor of Policing Practice Honours \line - Master of Policing Practice \cell \pard 

